# Nerva toolchain (Windows)

The compiler is not committed to git (~900 MB). After cloning:

  powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File scripts\bootstrap-toolchain.ps1

This downloads a pinned WinLibs build into toolchain/mingw64/ (gitignored).

Options:
  -Method download   fetch WinLibs zip (default for fresh clones)
  -Method junction   link to an existing winget WinLibs install (fast, no extra disk)
  -Method copy       full copy from winget install (offline-friendly)
  -Global            install under Program Files\Nerva and add user PATH

Then build:

  .\build.bat          (Windows — recommended)
  .\build.ps1
  make bootstrap-toolchain   # first time only, if make is available
  make test
